# HostOp Trial Rules

Use `AGENTS.md` as the canonical project context.

- Use pnpm for package commands.
- Keep all Supabase data org-scoped and backed by RLS.
- Preserve date filtering as `created_at >= start` and `created_at < end + 1 day`.
- Keep the selected date range persistent across dashboard and reservations pages.
- Keep PMS sync idempotent through `org_id,pms_reservation_id`.
- Do not commit `.env.local` or real credentials.
- Run `pnpm lint` and `pnpm build` before handoff.

Important files:

- `src/lib/data.ts`
- `src/lib/date-range.ts`
- `src/app/dashboard/page.tsx`
- `src/app/reservations/page.tsx`
- `src/app/api/sync-reservations/route.ts`
- `supabase/migrations/`
